Clinical, virological, and histologic evolution of hepatitis C virus infection 
in liver transplant recipients.

Lumbreras C(1), Colina F, Loinaz C, Domingo MJ, Fuertes A, Dominguez P, Gómez R, 
Aguado JM, Lizasoain M, González-Pinto I, Garcia I, Moreno E, Noriega AR.

Author information:
(1)Infectious Diseases Unit, Hospital Universitario Doce de Octubre, Universidad 
