Kraft W(1), Danckert D.

Author information:
(1)I. Medizinischen Tierklinik, Ludwig-Maximilians-Universität München.

The dogs and cats, treated at the Clinic of Internal Medicine of the University 
of Munich since 1983 show a tendency to a higher age of life; this is true 
